pullrequest.title: Do not export urdf symbols in sdformat 1.4 (-> sdf_1.4)

content.raw: Another person confirmed the bug via mail to me and I was able to get access to a testing case. The problem seems to be solved for me after replacing the sdformat in ROS by one built using this pull request.
